<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>INTERVIEW CANCELLATION NOTICE</title>
</head>

<body
    style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <div
        style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">

        <div style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #007bff; margin: 0;">INTERVIEW CANCELLATION NOTICE</h2>
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>Our HR team would like to inform you that the interview for <strong>{{title}}</strong> has been cancelled.</p>
        <p>We will contact you again if there is a new plan in the future. Thank you for your interest in this position.</p>
        <p>Best regards.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>